  <p>If you are a physician and would like to learn more about MedTogether and MTM, <%= link_to 'click here', static_pages_physician_path %></p>
  <p>If you are a health plan or government program administrator and would like to learn more about MedTogther and how it can help you serve your members, <%= link_to 'click here', static_pages_healthplan_path %></p>
